Problem Statement : Consumer Behavior Analysis
a. Identifying emerging trends and shifts in consumer preferences.
b. Assessing the impact of consumer sentiment on market dynamics and sector performance.
c. Evaluating the resilience of consumer-facing industries to economic downturns and disruptions.

Datasets to be used:

	Federal Reserve Economic Data (FRED)	Economic Indicators
Online Shopping Data	E-commerce platforms	Amazon, eBay, Shopify

	Market research firms	eMarketer, Statista

Social Media Data	Twitter API	Twitter Developer Platform

	Facebook Graph API	Facebook for Developers

	Instagram Graph API	Instagram for Developers

Demographic Data	U.S. Census Bureau	American Community Survey (ACS)
	National statistical agencies (other countries)	Varies by country
	Market research firms	Varies by provider
Credit Card Transaction Data	Credit card companies	Varies by credit card issuer
	Third-party data providers	Varies by provider
Housing Market Data	National Association of Realtors (NAR)	Housing Market Reports
	Real estate websites (e.g., Zillow, Realtor.com)	Zillow, Realtor.com

	Government agencies (e.g., HUD)	U.S. Department of Housing and Urban Development (HUD)

Travel and Leisure Data	Airlines, hotels, travel booking platforms	Varies by provider
	Tourism boards, government agencies	Varies by country or region
	Market research firms	Varies by provider
Survey Data	Market research firms	Varies by provider
	Government agencies	Varies by country or region
	Academic institutions	Varies by institution




